data.description:
VA Assumable Rate: 2.75% 

This updated 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem located in Glynlea Park (No HOA) is a true Jacksonville 1950s treasure with all of the style updates of 2020. Convenient to all of Jacksonville- less than 10 minutes from downtown and a short 25-minute drive to the beach.

Inside you'll notice the seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The open-concept design creates a welcoming and spacious atmosphere for entertaining. At the heart of this home is a spacious white shaker style kitchen, complete with granite countertops and matching stainless steel appliances. 
This home has luxury vinyl plank throughout makes cleaning a breeze while the split floorplan ensures privacy for the 4 bedrooms. The primary has plenty of space to include a larger closet and ensuite with walk-in shower. 

Step outside onto the huge screened-in back porch, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or evening cocktails while overlooking the large fenced backyard. The possibilities are endless for outdoor activities, from gardening to family barbecues. Plus, with a brand new roof installed Oct 2023 and an HVAC system replaced in 2020, you can move in with peace of mind knowing that your home is in great condition.

With over 1600 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room to accommodate your needs. And if you're stationed at NAS Jax or NS Mayport, you'll love the convenience of being less than 30 minutes away from both bases.
